<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>Gc - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/gc/</link><description>Gc - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/gc/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>JVM与系统问题排查</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7/jvm%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%8E%92%E6%9F%A5/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7/jvm%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%8E%92%E6%9F%A5/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="jvm与系统问题排查">JVM与系统问题排查</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：JVM问题排查遵循&quot;监控发现→日志定位→工具分析→验证修复&quot;的流程，CPU高通常与热点代码或死循环有关，内存泄漏需通过堆dump分析对象引用链，GC问题需结合日志和可视化工具判断。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="jvm问题排查遵循从监控到工具分析的系统化流程cpu内存gc是三大核心排查方向">JVM问题排查遵循从监控到工具分析的系统化流程，CPU、内存、GC是三大核心排查方向</h2>
<h3 id="cpu高排查流程">CPU高排查流程</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">1. 定位高CPU进程
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   top / htop → 找到PID
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">2. 定位高CPU线程
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   top -Hp PID → 找到TID
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   printf &#34;%x\n&#34; TID → 转换为十六进制
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">3. 查看线程堆栈
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   jstack PID | grep TID_HEX -A 30
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">4. 分析热点代码
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - 某方法执行时间长 → 优化算法
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - 频繁GC → 调整GC参数或内存
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - 死循环 → 修复代码</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="内存泄漏排查">内存泄漏排查</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">1. 发现内存增长
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   jstat -gcutil PID 1000 → 观察老年代增长
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">2. 生成堆dump
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   jmap -dump:format=b,file=heap.hprof PID
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   或 -XX:+HeapDumpOnOutOfMemoryError
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">3. 分析dump文件
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   MAT（Eclipse Memory Analyzer）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - Dominator Tree：查看大对象
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - Path to GC Roots：查看引用链
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - Leak Suspects：自动泄漏报告
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">常见泄漏源：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 静态集合缓存未清理
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- ThreadLocal未remove
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 未关闭的资源（流、连接）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 监听器未注销</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="gc问题排查">GC问题排查</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">1. 启用GC日志
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   -Xlog:gc*:file=gc.log:time:filecount=5,filesize=100m
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">2. 分析GC日志
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - GCeasy（在线工具）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - gceasy.io
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - GCViewer（本地工具）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">3. 关键指标
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - GC频率：多久一次
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - GC耗时：STW时间
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - 内存回收率：每次回收多少
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - 晋升速率：对象进入老年代速度
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">调优方向：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 堆太小 → 频繁GC → 增大堆
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 年轻代太小 → 对象过早晋升 → 增大新生代
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 大对象多 → 分配失败 → 调整大对象阈值</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 id="常用排查命令速查">常用排查命令速查</h2>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>问题</th>
          <th>命令</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>CPU高</td>
          <td>top + jstack</td>
          <td>定位线程和热点代码</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>内存占用</td>
          <td>jmap -heap</td>
          <td>堆内存分布</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>内存泄漏</td>
          <td>jmap -dump + MAT</td>
          <td>分析对象引用</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>GC情况</td>
          <td>jstat -gcutil</td>
          <td>实时GC统计</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>线程死锁</td>
          <td>jstack -l</td>
          <td>查看死锁信息</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>类加载</td>
          <td>jcmd PID VM.classloader_stats</td>
          <td>类加载器统计</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>系统调用</td>
          <td>strace -p PID</td>
          <td>跟踪系统调用</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>网络连接</td>
          <td>netstat -anp / ss -s</td>
          <td>连接状态统计</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<hr>
<h2 id="参考">参考</h2>
<ul>
