<li><a href="../../%e5%9f%ba%e7%a1%80%e7%9f%a5%e8%af%86/%e6%93%8d%e4%bd%9c%e7%b3%bb%e7%bb%9f/CPU%e8%b0%83%e5%ba%a6.md" rel="">CPU调度与上下文切换</a></li>
<li><a href="./CAT%e7%9b%91%e6%8e%a7.md" rel="">CAT分布式监控</a></li>
</ul>]]></description></item><item><title>JVM原理</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80/jvm%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80/jvm%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="jvm原理">JVM原理</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：JVM通过类加载机制将字节码转换为运行时结构，在堆/栈/方法区组成的内存模型中执行，GC自动管理堆内存生命周期，理解这三者的交互是JVM调优的基础。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="jvm由类加载子系统运行时数据区执行引擎三部分组成共同完成字节码到机器码的执行">JVM由类加载子系统、运行时数据区、执行引擎三部分组成，共同完成字节码到机器码的执行</h2>
<h3 id="类加载机制双亲委派模型保证核心类库安全">类加载机制：双亲委派模型保证核心类库安全</h3>
<p>类加载过程分七个阶段，其中<strong>加载、验证、准备、解析、初始化</strong>五个阶段是核心：</p>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">加载 → 验证 → 准备 → 解析 → 初始化 → 使用 → 卸载</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>双亲委派模型</strong>：</p>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">自定义类加载器
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↑ 委派
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">应用类加载器 (AppClassLoader)    - classpath
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↑ 委派
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">扩展类加载器 (ExtClassLoader)    - ext目录
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↑ 委派
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">启动类加载器 (Bootstrap)         - &lt;JAVA_HOME&gt;/lib</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 打破双亲委派：自定义类加载器直接加载</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">class</span> <span class="nc">CustomClassLoader</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">extends</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ClassLoader</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nd">@Override</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kd">protected</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Class</span><span class="o">&lt;?&gt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">loadClass</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">String</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">name</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">boolean</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">resolve</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">throws</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ClassNotFoundException</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="c1">// 先自己尝试加载，找不到再委派给父类</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="n">Class</span><span class="o">&lt;?&gt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">clazz</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">findLoadedClass</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">name</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">clazz</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">null</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">            </span><span class="n">clazz</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">findClass</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">name</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// 自定义加载逻辑</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">            </span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">clazz</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">null</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">                </span><span class="n">clazz</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">super</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">loadClass</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">name</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">resolve</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// 委派父类</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">            </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">clazz</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="运行时数据区堆存对象栈存帧方法区存元数据">运行时数据区：堆存对象、栈存帧、方法区存元数据</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>区域</th>
          <th>线程共享</th>
          <th>存储内容</th>
          <th>溢出表现</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>堆（Heap）</td>
          <td>是</td>
          <td>对象实例、数组</td>
          <td><code>OutOfMemoryError: Java heap space</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>虚拟机栈</td>
          <td>否</td>
          <td>栈帧（局部变量、操作数栈）</td>
          <td><code>StackOverflowError</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>本地方法栈</td>
          <td>否</td>
          <td>Native方法执行</td>
          <td>同虚拟机栈</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>程序计数器</td>
          <td>否</td>
          <td>当前执行字节码地址</td>
          <td>不会溢出</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>方法区（Metaspace）</td>
          <td>是</td>
          <td>类元数据、常量池</td>
          <td><code>OutOfMemoryError: Metaspace</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>直接内存</td>
          <td>是</td>
          <td>NIO的Buffer</td>
          <td><code>OutOfMemoryError: Direct buffer memory</code></td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 栈帧结构示意</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">methodA</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">x</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">10</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">              </span><span class="c1">// 局部变量表</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">methodB</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">               </span><span class="c1">// 操作数栈压入返回地址</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">methodB</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">Object</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">obj</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Object</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// obj引用在栈，对象在堆</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
